{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water in mixing bowl and bring to the boil <b>10 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>, or until boiling.","Add orzo, 1 tbsp oil and salt then cook <b>7 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid.","Drain and rinse orzo through simmering basket, then transfer into a large serving bowl, drizzle orzo with remaining 1 tbsp oil and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place parsley in mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. Parsley should be a fine consistency. Repeat chopping if necesasary.","Add feta and artichokes then chop <b>2 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer into serving bowl with orzo and set aside.","Place the large serving bowl onto mixing bowl lid, then weigh pine nuts and sun-dried tomatoes into it.","Add chickpeas, lemon juice and pepper to serving bowl, then stir well with spatula to combine. Serve salad garnished with extra parsley leaves."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1100 g water","400 g orzo, rinsed and drained","2 tbsp extra virgin olive oil","½ tsp fine sea salt, to taste","4 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only, plus extra leaves for garnishing","130 g feta cheese, in pieces","340 g marinated artichoke hearts, drained","60 g pine nuts, toasted","100 g sun-dried tomatoes, cut into thin slices","400 g canned chickpeas, rinsed and drained (weight is pre-draining)","1 tbsp lemon juice","1 pinch ground black pepper, to taste"]}],"id":"r123590","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-meES6ZDTWM4\/XZWYmXazBlI\/AAAAAAAAeAs\/Y3oZl7jZCs4D4ASZ4uQOlgn90YcINWiPACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_FVKfYd7MPIFcoyPT.png","title":"Orzo Salad with Artichoke and Feta","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"30 g","fat":"25 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"96 g","calories":"3281 kJ \/ 781 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large serving bowl","basicInfo":["easy","15m","25m","4 portions"]}